{"tid":594144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英美德法罕有發聯合聲明　指俄國要為斯科利帕事件負責","createTime":"2018-03-15T15:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T05:08:18.000Z","uid":147314,"like":58,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"d12932940b0d856ca8e41ee9cb7970f6f1ba33e7","tid":594144,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T15:00:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1386073-20180315.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1386073-20180315.htm&d=3CbmPWHc0YoSZgGaxrV5U57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c1103ad4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1386073-20180315.htm&h=8d8e91d8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1386073-20180315.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n英美德法罕有發聯合聲明　指俄國要為斯科利帕事件負責<br />\n2018-03-15 HKT 21:41<br />\n<br />\n美國、法國、德國和英國，罕有發表聯合聲明，共同指摘俄羅斯，沒有就前特工斯科利帕父女在英國被企圖毒殺的案件，作出合理解釋，認為俄方要為事件負責。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，今次非法使用化武的行為，是「對英國主權的攻擊」和「違反國際法」。<br />\n<br />\n英國早前宣布，驅逐23名俄羅斯外交官，暫停與俄羅斯的雙邊接觸。莫斯科就宣布，將驅逐英國外交人員作為報復，並將很快作出行動。"},{"pid":"6a9babd2db4c396d454241fdb85c27d54adb8ffd","tid":594144,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T15:05:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b2d17356735693f36cc5b0421ff9663c54cb5d","tid":594144,"uid":39698,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T15:07:24.000Z","msg":"ww3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3908e198b0e44a1a1330a798df8c2f342ca01300","tid":594144,"uid":37735,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"拉隊走人 唔踢世界盃<br />\n<br />\n等俄羅斯 搞世盃的錢燒哂去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad67e89d2e069a82d6c18fba656748bd4a011fb","tid":59414